OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be cloudy for Dumfries,
OL,6,FGalloway and western Borders with
OL,7,Frain, heavy at times. Variable cloud
OL,8,Fwith some occasional brightness and
OL,9,Fmostly dry for Edinburgh, Lothian and
OL,10,Feastern Borders, though some outbreaks
OL,11,Fof rain possible at times. Mild.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FQuite cloudy through the
OL,14,Fevening and overnight with some
OL,15,Fshowery rain, heavy at times. Some
OL,16,Fdrier and clearer spells developing
OL,17,Ftowards morning. Windy at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
