OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA dry, bright start in the
OL,6,Feast, becoming cloudy through the
OL,7,Fmorning with patchy rain. Cloudy with
OL,8,Foccasionally heavy rain in west.
OL,9,FBecoming dry with clear spells in
OL,10,Fevening. Breezy.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FCloudy
OL,13,Fwith rain on Friday morning, becoming
OL,14,Fbrighter with a few showers later.
OL,15,FBright for most of Saturday, rain
OL,16,Farriving later. Cloudy and breezy with
OL,17,Foutbreaks of rain on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
